## Usage (command-line)
```
usage: mvodb [-h] [-y] FILE [FILE ...]

positional arguments:
  FILE              Files to move/rename.

optional arguments:
  -h, --help        show this help message and exit
  -y, --no-confirm  Do not ask confirmation.

```



